    "Capacity Equipment Design Optimization: In wind power scenarios, generative AI optimizes the design of wind turbine blades by simulating various wind environments and assessing performance, allowing engineers to iteratively refine blade design parameters.",
    "This includes adapting to unique regional environmental features, rapidly improving the adaptability of power generation equipment and increasing energy efficiency.",
    "Power Plant Model Design: For solar power system planning, generative AI utilizes realworld survey data from drones, combining environmental factors like sunlight, shadows, and climate to automatically generate layout and electrical connection designs in CAD software.",
    "Tools like Dassault Systèmes' CATIA can automate electrical system design in complex environments, creating precise and professional plans.",
